releaseNotes:
## What's Changed
* Added checkout options by @Kiryuumaru in https://github.com/Kiryuumaru/NukeBuildHelpers/pull/98
* Updated `TestEntry.md`, `BuildEntry.md` and `PublishEntry.md` by @Kiryuumaru in https://github.com/Kiryuumaru/NukeBuildHelpers/pull/99
* Fixed local run by @Kiryuumaru in https://github.com/Kiryuumaru/NukeBuildHelpers/pull/100
* Added matrix feature by @Kiryuumaru in https://github.com/Kiryuumaru/NukeBuildHelpers/pull/101
* Added customizable workflow id by @Kiryuumaru in https://github.com/Kiryuumaru/NukeBuildHelpers/pull/102
* Fixed invalid cache move by @Kiryuumaru in https://github.com/Kiryuumaru/NukeBuildHelpers/pull/103
* Fixed recursive move dir on symbolic links by @Kiryuumaru in https://github.com/Kiryuumaru/NukeBuildHelpers/pull/104
* Fixed copy invalid pathing by @Kiryuumaru in https://github.com/Kiryuumaru/NukeBuildHelpers/pull/105
* Fixed junction symbolic link recursive moving by @Kiryuumaru in https://github.com/Kiryuumaru/NukeBuildHelpers/pull/106
* Fixed null or invalid symbolic links on recursive move or copy by @Kiryuumaru in https://github.com/Kiryuumaru/NukeBuildHelpers/pull/107
* Fixed operations copy, move and delete on recursive symbolic links by @Kiryuumaru in https://github.com/Kiryuumaru/NukeBuildHelpers/pull/109
* Added workflow config entry by @Kiryuumaru in https://github.com/Kiryuumaru/NukeBuildHelpers/pull/110
* Bump YamlDotNet from 15.3.0 to 16.0.0 by @dependabot in https://github.com/Kiryuumaru/NukeBuildHelpers/pull/108
* Fixed github workflow generation on runs-on property by @Kiryuumaru in https://github.com/Kiryuumaru/NukeBuildHelpers/pull/111
* Fixed github self-hosted runner error on workflow build by @Kiryuumaru in https://github.com/Kiryuumaru/NukeBuildHelpers/pull/112
* Added docs `WorkflowConfigEntry.md` by @Kiryuumaru in https://github.com/Kiryuumaru/NukeBuildHelpers/pull/113
* Added timeout to pre setup and post setup jobs by @Kiryuumaru in https://github.com/Kiryuumaru/NukeBuildHelpers/pull/114
* Added Run subcommand by @Kiryuumaru in https://github.com/Kiryuumaru/NukeBuildHelpers/pull/115
* Fixed local runs by @Kiryuumaru in https://github.com/Kiryuumaru/NukeBuildHelpers/pull/116
* Fixed post setup artifacts prepare by @Kiryuumaru in https://github.com/Kiryuumaru/NukeBuildHelpers/pull/117
* Fixed workflow default naming on matrix by @Kiryuumaru in https://github.com/Kiryuumaru/NukeBuildHelpers/pull/118

## New Versions
* Bump `nuke_build_helpers` from `4.2.0-prerelease.9` to `4.9.4-prerelease.1`. See [changelog](https://github.com/Kiryuumaru/NukeBuildHelpers/compare/nuke_build_helpers/4.2.0-prerelease.9...nuke_build_helpers/4.9.4-prerelease.1)


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/Kiryuumaru/NukeBuildHelpers/compare/build.420...build.445
